data.description: Large home on mature lot.  Featuring 3 beds, 2 full baths, and an oversized great room.  Stainless steel appliances, new paint on the interior and trim, and hardwood floors throughout all main areas.  1.5 acres features mature trees, several fruiting trees, 2 driveways and a 2 car garage for storing all your toys.  Motivated seller offering up to $10,000 in concessions towards leach field repairs!
